title: When looking for pybind11, do not attempt to get properties from pybind11:pybind11.
body_html: There is no property name "INTERFACE_INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES" for pybind11::pybind11. This will cause cmake error if there exists a system installation of pybind11. In addition, pybind11_INCLUDE_DIRS is already set once "find_package(pybind11 CONFIG)" finds pybind11.
